APPRAISE GOODS: Estimating an item's fair value

Category: Trade
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Looking over an item and judging what it is actually worth, rather
than what a seller claims it is worth. Covers general goods rather
than a specialist's narrow expertise (see Recognize Gems and
Recognize Weapon Quality for those).

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, barter, recognize gems, recognize weapon quality
